{"tid":934533,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人啲老母都係咁樣","createTime":"2018-12-09T10:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T10:54:00.000Z","uid":172024,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f5c465d2c919024f1f9875cd04afae41fa6dd3","tid":934533,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:45:49.000Z","msg":"話說同屋企人去旅行 <br />\n我同老豆就食乜都可以既 <br />\n老母就比較picky <br />\n所以事前一定會問佢想食乜先 <br />\n問佢又話無所謂 <br />\n到去揀好間餐廳 <br />\n又嫌呢嫌路<br />\n係咁聽佢嘰哩咕嚕都算 <br />\n仲要黑口黑面 <br />\n擺哂款 比說話個職員聽 <br />\n救命 真係有啲覺得收家<br />\n每次出街食飯就特別勞氣同多事發生 <br />\n又無人得罪佢 嬲埋啲理解唔到既位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一家人出街食一餐飯都好辛苦"},{"pid":"2ea9b758998e28e62d2c22f09879217423888d22","tid":934533,"uid":117967,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:51:19.000Z","msg":"你老母抵屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112d6635584fd2930d8aa9976d7219d169b26ef5","tid":934533,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"picky"}]}